            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後跌幅擴大，最多跌606點或2.34%，報25282，現報25299，跌588點或2.27%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跌229點或3.83% ，報5773; 恒生國企指數跌227點或2.45%，報5773。 </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交2384.79億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)跌4.47%，報154元 ; 騰訊(00700)跌2.18%，報606.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(00981)跌6.16%，報69.35元 ; 華虹(01347)挫6.88%，報75.85元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中興通訊(00763)大瀉13.62%，報37.16元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥捷安康(02617)逆市飆27.03%，報211元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪電子(00285)插8.37%，報37.64元，為表現最差藍籌股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周大福(01929)升5.28%，報16.56元 ; 老鋪黃金(06181)升2.43%，報823元，成交入20大。</p>\n</div>",
